31 years since AIDS has occurred in the world, or at least since the first documented cases," says Jaime Andrade Villanueva, head of the HIV Unit at the Civil Hospital in Guadalajara, who is a very successful patient who will start treatment in a timely and appropriate manner, says Jaime Andrade Villanueva, head of the HIV Unit in Guadalajara, and that this information was confirmed in a prestigious scientific publication in April this year.
